{
  "id" : 740,
  "songNumber" : 128,
  "title" : "AM I A SOLDIER OF THE CROSS",
  "language" : "english",
  "capo" : 0,
  "bpm" : 0,
  "timeSignature" : "4/4",
  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Am I a soldier of the cross,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "A follower of the Lamb,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 18
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And shall I fear to own His cause,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 12
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 28
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Or blush to speak His Name?",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 12
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "And when the battle's over, we shall wear a crown!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 44
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Yes, we shall wear a crown! Yes, we shall wear a crown!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 14
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 49
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And when the battle's over, we shall wear a crown",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 44
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In the new Jerusalem.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 15
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Wear a crown, wear a crown,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 21
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Wear a bright and shining crown.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 26
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And when the battle's over, we shall wear a crown"
    }, {
      "text" : "In the new Jerusalem."
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Must I be carried to the skies",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "On flow'ry beds of ease,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "While others fought to win the prize,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 31
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And sailed through bloody seas ?",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Are there no foes for me to face?",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Must I not stem the flood?",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Is this vile world a friend to grace",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 13
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 31
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "To help me on to God?",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 11
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Sure I must fight if I would reign,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 12
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Increase my courage, Lord,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 21
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I'll bear the toil, endure the pain,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 14
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 31
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Supported by Thy Word.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    } ]
  } ]
}